In the end, I'd say Risk vs Reward is good, even if some parts can be a pain in the ass. <p><p><font face="verdana, arial" size="-2"><u><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6885" target=top>Gerald Swiftblades</a></u> [<a href="http://www.darkblood.com" target=top><i>Darkblood</i></a>]<br>
